            . I am a pawnbroker, I received a piece of tammy of Richardson, on the 3d of February (producing it) I lent four shillings and sixpence upon it, I never saw nor heard of White;</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. They appear to me to be tore one from the other; I believe they are mine, the marks that were on them are demolished, but I cannot positively say: it is tore into remnants, the whole piece was about thirt-ysix yards.</p>
